# Analyzer Definition

**Who:** Analyzer tool (e.g., ArchitectTasksAnalyzerTool)
**What:** Performs static or dynamic analysis to find issues or gather metrics
**When:** On demand, scheduled, or as part of CI
**Where:** Used in all or specific projects (document here)
**Why:** To identify bugs, performance issues, or code quality problems
**How:** Examines code or runtime behavior, reports findings
